      <title>美国银行的莫伊尼汉认为交易“充满热情”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/bofa-s-moynihan-sees-lots-of-enthusiasm-for-deals-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席执行官布莱恩·莫伊尼汉讨论了当前的投资环境以及他在这家银行巨头的未来。莫伊尼汉在瑞士达沃斯举行的世界经济论坛年会上接受彭博电视台采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/bofa-s-moynihan-sees-lots-of-enthusiasm-for-deals-video</guid>
